        "subject": "LU-3967 lprocfs: Add history support for lprocfs_stats",
        "message": "LU-3967 lprocfs: Add history support for lprocfs_stats\n\nThis patch helps to collect the stats during some time intervals.\nWhen enabled, it collects stats every 10 seconds and keeps the\ncounts during last 10 seconds, 100 seconds and 10000 seconds by\ndefault. The time intervals can be modified when inserting module.\n\nSigned-off-by: Li Xi <lixi@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I6a8aa65d3847bcde432e50ad556098cdf74ccbee\n"
      },
